description: Retrieves the properties associated with import model job, including the status of the job. For more information, see Import a customized model in the Amazon Bedrock User Guide.

parameters.name: jobIdentifier
parameters.description: The identifier of the import job.

nested_items.name: jobArn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the import job.

nested_items.name: jobName
nested_items.description: The name of the import job.

nested_items.name: importedModelName
nested_items.description: The name of the imported model.

nested_items.name: importedModelArn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the imported model.

nested_items.name: roleArn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the IAM role associated with this job.

nested_items.name: modelDataSource
nested_items.description: The data source for the imported model.

nested_items.name: s3DataSource
nested_items.description: The Amazon S3 data source of the imported model.

nested_items.name: s3Uri
nested_items.description: The URI of the Amazon S3 data source.

nested_items.name: status
nested_items.description: The status of the job. A successful job transitions from in-progress to completed when the imported model is ready to use. If the job failed, the failure message contains information about why the job failed.

nested_items.name: failureMessage
nested_items.description: Information about why the import job failed.

nested_items.name: creationTime
nested_items.description: The time the resource was created.

nested_items.name: lastModifiedTime
nested_items.description: Time the resource was last modified.

nested_items.name: endTime
nested_items.description: Time that the resource transitioned to terminal state.

nested_items.name: vpcConfig
nested_items.description: The Virtual Private Cloud (VPC) configuration of the import model job.

nested_items.name: subnetIds
nested_items.description: An array of IDs for each subnet in the VPC to use.

nested_items.name: securityGroupIds
nested_items.description: An array of IDs for each security group in the VPC to use.

nested_items.name: importedModelKmsKeyArn
nested_items.description: The imported model is encrypted at rest using this key.
